{"tid":1320014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新戰略行動-[關愛動物委員會]","createTime":"2019-07-15T09:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T07:16:28.000Z","uid":244876,"like":32,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"93c6ef56f2169ebf4db192c05e763c9ff42291f0","tid":1320014,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:40:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的，孔子報夢比左個姜子牙再報比身處南蠻之地既巴打聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日其實睇到狗狗聽主人唔同指令實在好大壓力，應該就來爆煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴晚有d狗仔唔聽爸爸媽媽話自己衝左出去玩，搞到成身傷曬。<br />\n真係好陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拿我就冇養過狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最多兔仔姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。要知道人同動物唔開心啊，憤怒啊，都係有原因既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔識狗仔點解情緒咁差，緊係要搵傳心師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地實聽得明發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，係咪主人教得唔好?係咪想搞野冇得搞?係咪冇啖好食?定係長時間冇教好訓?<br />\n<br />\n傳心師所以就好重要，唔知狗仔諗咩最後比錯解決方法，咪搞到狗仔亂咁咬野，周圍大小二便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到人人都驚仲點會同佢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳心師最好緊係靚女，靚女都係特別有種令人覺得好舒服既氣質，搵佢地傾計實特別放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有咩壓力唔開心講完點都舒服好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係要搞我同意有D難,因為要快同PLAN同時做<br />\n<br />\n始終狗仔真係唔聽話最多棄養比愛協姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bee236e8e99ec3af2e6f4e7189bca3452327e1e","tid":1320014,"uid":263464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:42:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8